{
  "stem": "13600.4",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 126,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But they approached us, of course, and then made a dent in the ship, and stopped it, and came in the-- there was a bit of a struggle.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 126,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "A few people were killed, and a number were injured.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 127,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Boarded the boat, yes.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 127,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And took us in tow to Haifa.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 128,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "In Haifa, there was not a person to be seen, because the British announced that nobody should get out of their homes.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 129,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "A curfew.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 130,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "--landed in Haifa, not seeing one person civil, except the British army.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 131,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We were taken in-- in three ships, 1,500 on each.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 132,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "In the same day.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 133,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "In the same day.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 133,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "In the same day.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 134,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "That's correct.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 135,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "A boat, it was-- that was not made for people, for passengers.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 135,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It was just a deep hull, you know, and people were in there.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 135,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I somehow again organized myself to be on top.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 135,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I don't remember how.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 135,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I don't know.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 135,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But I-- I was lying on top in the boat.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 136,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I don't know how.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 137,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "--where there was a bit of air.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 138,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "That's correct.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 139,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The same place.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 140,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Same ship.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 141,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "On the ship?",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 141,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Very bad.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 141,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It was hot.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 141,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "It was July.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 141,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] No change of clothes.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 141,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "No water-- I mean, for washing, yes.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 142,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I will tell you, coming from Russia, you have to realize that everything pales.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 142,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So I-- personally, I don't see them as very bad.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 142,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I don't have bad experience.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 142,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I will tell you why.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 142,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I had very little knowledge of English.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 142,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "In Russian, you couldn't speak to them.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 142,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Neither German.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 142,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Very little knowledge.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 142,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "But a few words I started commanding.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 142,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And being on top, I approached where there was-- the kitchen was.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 142,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And I told them, I want to go in there.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 142,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "I don't-- under what pretext-- pretext.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 142,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And I got back with some [?",
      "word_count": 7
    }
  ],
